**Describe the bug**
After adding an image to an word document using open xml sdk 2.7.1,
the user can't use the document because it has "unreadable content".
Without adding an image and only changing text, no error occurs.
The code to add the image is from the microsoft example.
(https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/office/open-xml/how-to-insert-a-picture-into-a-word-processing-document)

I already tried using the open xml sdk 2.5 productivity tool, but it shows 35 errors.
Even after saving it as a normal document (clicking yes in the document on the error dialog),
 the tool shows 35 errors.

**Screenshots**
If applicable, add screenshots to help explain your problem.
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/61208946/235175121-5faf1e63-8a51-40db-b8c9-7520d2c37454.png)
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/61208946/235175179-be6904bb-ebb4-4f7e-90d1-e9719d4d7d64.png)


**To Reproduce**
```
 using (WordprocessingDocument document = WordprocessingDocument.Open(@"C:\PROJEKTE\KUNDEN_REPOS\kiepe\OPEN_XML\Servicebericht23.docx", true))
                {
                    var elementsBody = document.MainDocumentPart.Document.Body;

                    Table table = document.MainDocumentPart.Document.Body.Elements<Table>().ElementAt(1);
                    var tableRow = table.Elements<DocumentFormat.OpenXml.Wordprocessing.TableRow>().ElementAt(1);
                    DocumentFormat.OpenXml.Wordprocessing.TableCell c = tableRow.Elements<DocumentFormat.OpenXml.Wordprocessing.TableCell>().ElementAt(0);
                    c.RemoveAllChildren();

                    var mainPart = document.MainDocumentPart;
                    ImagePart imagePart = mainPart.AddImagePart(ImagePartType.Png);

                    using (FileStream stream = new FileStream(@"C:\Users\voigt\Pictures\CloseIcon.png", FileMode.Open))
                    {
                        imagePart.FeedData(stream);
                    }

                    AddImageToCell(c, mainPart.GetIdOfPart(imagePart), 2638425L, 1758950L, 2638623L, 1759082L, 1, $"Bild_1.png");

                    document.Save();
                    document.Close();
}

     private static void AddImageToCell(DocumentFormat.OpenXml.Wordprocessing.TableCell cell, string relationshipId)
        {
            var element = new DocumentFormat.OpenXml.Wordprocessing.Drawing(
              new DW.Inline(
                  new DW.Extent()
                  {
                      Cx = 2638425L,
                      Cy = 628650L
                  },
                  new DW.EffectExtent() { LeftEdge = 0L, TopEdge = 0L, RightEdge = 0L, BottomEdge = 6350L },
                  new DW.DocProperties() { Id = 2U, Name = "Picture 1" },
                  new DW.NonVisualGraphicFrameDrawingProperties(new A.GraphicFrameLocks() { NoChangeAspect = true, NoResize = false, NoSelection = false }),
                  new A.Graphic(new A.GraphicData(new PIC.Picture(
                              new PIC.NonVisualPictureProperties(
                                  new PIC.NonVisualDrawingProperties()
                                  {
                                      Id = 1U,
                                      Name = "image.png"
                                  },
                                  new PIC.NonVisualPictureDrawingProperties()),
                              new PIC.BlipFill(
                                  new A.Blip(
                                      new A.BlipExtensionList(
                                          new A.BlipExtension()
                                          {
                                              Uri = "{28A0092B-C50C-407E-A947-70E740481C1C}"
                                          }))
                                  {
                                      Embed = relationshipId,
                                      CompressionState = A.BlipCompressionValues.Print
                                  },
                                  new A.Stretch(new A.FillRectangle())),
                              new PIC.ShapeProperties(
                                  new A.Transform2D(new A.Offset() { X = 0L, Y = 0L }, new A.Extents() { Cx = 2638631L, Cy = 628699L }),
                                  new A.PresetGeometry(new A.AdjustValueList()) { Preset = A.ShapeTypeValues.Rectangle })))
                  {
                      Uri = "http://schemas.openxmlformats.org/drawingml/2006/picture"
                  }))
              {
                  DistanceFromTop = 0U,
                  DistanceFromBottom = 0U,
                  DistanceFromLeft = 0U,
                  DistanceFromRight = 0U,
                  EditId = "50D07946"
              });

            cell.Append(new DocumentFormat.OpenXml.Wordprocessing.Paragraph(new DocumentFormat.OpenXml.Wordprocessing.Run(element)));
        }

```

Steps to reproduce the behavior:
1. Open document "Servicebericht23.docx" using open xml sdk
2. get the second table (index 1)
3. get the second row
4. remove all children
5. add an image (png)
6. save the document

**Observed behavior**
The document has no readable content and shows an error to the user.

**Expected behavior**
The document can be opened without error.

**Desktop (please complete the following information):**
 - OS: Windows 10 Pro 22H2
 - Office version: Microsoft® Word für Microsoft 365 MSO (Version 2303 Build 16.0.16227.20202) 64 Bit 
 - .NET Target: NET Framework 4.6.2 / console application
 - DocumentFormat.OpenXml Version: 2.7.1 

**Additional context**
[Servicebericht23.docx](https://github.com/dotnet/Open-XML-SDK/files/11354511/Servicebericht23.docx)
